# ============================================================
#  .gitignore — protect privacy / unpublished work / secrets
# ============================================================

# ── secrets / credentials — NEVER commit ──────────────────
.env
**/.env
*.pem
*_secret*
*api_key*

# ── unpublished / personal — NEVER publish ────────────────
paper/
**/paper/
follow-on/
**/follow-on/
K99_*
**/K99_*
*[Ss]pecific_[Aa]ims*
DESIGN_NOTES.md
**/DESIGN_NOTES.md
03_SYNTHESIZED_aims_FINAL.md
*Research proposal*.pdf
*RESEARCH STRATEGY*.pdf
*Research_Description*.pdf
*MINFLUX*
*.docx

# ── personal voice recordings (your own voice) ────────────
**/voice/*.wav
**/voice/*.mp3
**/voice/_wav/
**/voice_reference*
**/ref_*.wav

# ── large / regenerable outputs (regenerate via SESSION_LOG.md) ──
*.dcd
*.xtc
*.trr
*.h5
outputs/**/*.cif
outputs/**/*.pdb
**/trajectories/

# ── generated audio/video (large, regenerable) ────────────
**/audio/*.mp3
**/audio/*.aiff
**/video/*.mp4
**/video/_clips*/
**/voice_xtts/
**/voice_eleven/

# ── system / python ───────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
*.sb-*/
